    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You would have to build your own [custom widget](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#custom-widgets):\n\n``` js\nvar customWidget = {\n  init: function(options) {\n    $('x').onClick(function() {\n      options.helper.setQueryParameter('restrictSearchableAttributes', ...);\n    });\n  }\n};\n\nsearch.addWidget(customWidget);\n```\n\nLet me know.\n",
